# Installation

## From pip
The easiest way to install Carcar치 is with pip:

```python
pip install carcara
```

## From github
To install Carcar치 directly from the GitHub repository, run the following commands:

```python
pip install git+https://github.com/seixasgroup/carcara.git
```



